name: Toolkit
description: A rudimentary multi-function toolkit effective at hull mending. Compatible with repair drones and crewed EVA tasking.

name: Ammunition
description: The most basic form of space-grade ballistic ammunition. Compatible with kinetic type slotted weaponry. Weak against energy shielding, effective against hull plating.

name: Food
description: The latest in molecular gastronomic science. Who knew corn could taste this good? Effective in addressing minor homeostatic crew deficiencies.

name: Fuel
description: Basic hydrogen fuel cell replenishment. Low energy density, can be improved with further refinement.

name: Mining Drill Tier 2 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Mining Drill from Tier 1 to Tier 2.

name: Mining Drill Tier 3 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Mining Drill from Tier 2 to Tier 3.

name: Mining Drill Tier 4 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Mining Drill from Tier 3 to Tier 4.

name: Mining Drill Tier 5 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Mining Drill from Tier 4 to Tier 5.

name: Power Plant Tier 5 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Power Plant from Tier 4 to Tier 5.

name: Power Plant Tier 4 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Power Plant from Tier 3 to Tier 4.

name: Power Plant Tier 3 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Power Plant from Tier 2 to Tier 3.

name: Power Plant Tier 2 Upgrade Bundle
description: Resource bundle to upgrade a Power Plant from Tier 1 to Tier 2.

name: Lumanite
description: An uncommon crystal mostly found in the medium risk zone, Lumanite has a liquid metal core that, once agitated, creates electric energy. It’s often used to create emitters.

name: Arco
description: The fleeting Arco crystal has the ability to retain its sturdiness under high temperatures while also being efficient in dissipating kinetic energy.

name: Super Conductor
description: A product created to permit high conductivity in energy-demanding structures. It’s often used in crafting particle accelerators.

name: Biomass
description: Organic compounds of flora and fauna, which has intensive usage in farming and overall agriculture

name: Carbon
description: An abundant basic resource found throughout the galaxy and used in various applications.

name: Steel
description: A very resistant alloy made of Iron and Carbon. Steel is strong, tough, and ductile, allowing for its usage in a myriad of applications.

name: Crystal Lattice
description: An advanced molecular arrangement of crystals. Designed to absorb or modulate energy and allow its stable usage.

name: Electronics
description: A piece of active device used to induce energy flow.

name: Copper Wire
description: Galia’s most common electrical conductor. It’s used in many different applications ranging from power sources to electronics.

name: Iron Ore
description: Iron is a good conductor of heat, and electricity. It is extensively used to produce steel, metal alloys, and various components for the industry after refinement.

name: Power Source
description: A device crafted to store energy and distribute it to an electronic device.

name: Copper Ore
description: Copper has high durability and good corrosion resistance while maintaining high malleability, allowing it to be transformed into wires, blades, and other crafting components after refinement.

name: Magnet
description: Magnets are one of the most basic products. It has many applications due to its useful magnetic properties.

name: Radiation Absorber
description: A device used to control radiation emitted from high energy mechanisms.

name: Strange Emitter
description: A device crafted to harness Lumanite innate properties to emit strange energy. It’s often used in crafting particle accelerators.

name: Particle Accelerator
description: A device that uses EM-Strange fields to excite energy particles.

name: Graphene
description: Graphene has been perceived as a miraculous material since its discovery. Made from carbon compounds, it’s many times stronger than steel yet light and flexible. This material is frequently utilized in the current age.

name: Hydrocarbon
description: Hydrocarbons are oily substances that can be further refined or used as lubricant in various mechanisms.

name: Framework
description: A basic support structure. Ubiquitously used in industry.

name: Rochinol
description: The elusive Rochinol emits a bright purple color, which resembles the light of Iris. Being a piezoelectric material, it’s used to turn mechanical energy into electrical, enabling many different applications in manufacturing.

name: Copper
description: A refined copper bar. A highly malleable material used in various crafts of the galactic industries.

name: Diamond
description: The diamond is one of the sturdiest and most reflexive materials in the whole cosmos, giving it popularity as an ornament and in industry. It is specially used in the augmentation of deep mining drills.

name: Survey Data Unit
description: A data cube containing the most recent and accurate metrics, impressions, and observations around a Galia Expanse sector. It is highly coveted by those who know the price of information.

name: Hydrogen
description: Present in most living things. Hydrogen is now the principal resource for fueling the fleets of the galaxy and producing crystals lattices.

name: Polymer
description: Refined from hydrocarbon, polymers are low-cost, low-density, high-resistance materials with various use cases, ranging from packaging to 3D printing.

name: Energy Substrate
description: A product used to bind substrates in high-energy reactions. It’s often found in energy generation structures, especially on radiation absorbers.

name: Electromagnet
description: A powerful device that uses electric current and magnets create an electromagnetic field.

name: Iron
description: A refined iron bar. A reliable material used in various crafts of the galactic industries.

name: Council RFR 2023
description: A token voucher for a bundle of crafted goods requested by the Council of Peace security force to support the reconstruction efforts in the Medium Zone. Redeemable for ATLAS in the Galactic Marketplace.

name: Field Stabilizer
description: An electromagnetic field. Used to isolate an area from external elements' interference.

name: Aerogel
description: A chemical compound used in complex space infrastructure crafts.

name: Titanium
description: A standard bar of titanium, used in various recipes in the intergalactic industries.

name: Titanium Ore
description: Titanium is an outstanding metal that reunites various important properties for crafting, such as being very resistant, having low density, being resistant to heat deformation, and biocompatible.

name: Nitrogen
description: Nitrogen is one of the pillars of the galaxy’s chemical industry. It has uses in many different crafts, from producing transistors in electronics to enabling massive food production and preservation.

name: Silica
description: One of the most common crystals found throughout Galia Expanse. Silica has many applications in the industry as it’s formidable as a mechanical resonator and has pyroelectricity properties.

name: Golden Ticket 2624
description: A delicate card, interwoven with veins of luminescent gold, exchangeable for a chance in the galactical wheel of fortune. Its subtle glow is reminiscent of distant stars, captivating those who behold it. Upon its reverse, an inscription reads: “Certification of Condition Met - May the Cosmic Currents flow in your favor, issued during the Golden Carnival of 2624.”
